OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FWaitrose sorry after       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FChristmas advert criticism 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Waitrose has apologised after being    
OL,6, criticised by skin cancer patients and 
OL,7, a charity for its Christmas advert     
OL,8, showing farmers comparing sun tans.    
OL,10,FThe supermarket faced a backlash to its
OL,11,Fvideo on social media, with some people
OL,12,Fsaying a section of the advert         
OL,13,Fglorified sun tans and failed to       
OL,14,Fhighlight the dangers of sunlight.     
OL,16,F"Waitrose can do better than this,"    
OL,17,Fsaid charity Melanoma UK.              
OL,19,FThe grocer said it was "sorry for the  
OL,20,Fupset caused".                         
